e-ozzy-zakk-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ozzy-zakk-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ozzy-zakk-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ozzy-zakk-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a>的长期合作者和吉他手Zakk Wylde嘲笑主唱可以在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的最后一场演出的“王位上飞过体育场”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-interview-sharon-ozzy-osbourne-tony-iommi-health-birmingham-villa-park-final-show-new-material-3835523">沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne）和托尼·艾奥姆（Tony Iommi</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">这支传奇的金属乐队宣布了他们的最后一次现场表演的详细信息，该表演将于7月5日在伯明翰的别墅公园举行</a>。</p><p>除了包含原始的阵容 -  Ozzy， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-iommi">Tony Iommi</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geezer-butler">Geezer Butler</a>和Bill Ward之外，乐队还将加入一系列明星的开幕表演和特别嘉宾的名单，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Metallica">Metallica</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Slayer">Slayer</a> ，Slayer， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Pantera">Pantera</a> ，Pantera，Pantera， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Lamb-Of-God">lamb of God</a> ，Tool， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tool">Tool</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mastodon">Mastodon</a> ，Mastodon，Mastodon， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alice-In-Chains">Mastodon，Mastodon，Mastodon，Alice in Chains in Chains in Chains</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">n&#39;&#39;Ross n&#39;Ross n&#39;Ross&#39;Ross</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halestorm">Halestorm</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">gojira</a>和更多。</p><p> Wylde最近在谈到Riff X的<em>Metal XS</em>时说，演出的幅度将“令人振奋”，并分享了Ozzy如何在猛mm象音乐会中浏览的一些见解。</p><p>他说：“游戏计划是，希望这就是发生的事情，您总是必须保持生活的光明，因为绿野仙踪在<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rock/ozzy-osbourne-throne-black-sabbath-farewell-show-1235929718/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>摇滚</em></a>名人堂里唱歌。”</p><p> “奥兹（Ozzy）只是坐在椅子上，他在唱歌&#39;妈妈，我要回家&#39;，听起来很棒。所以希望我们会做到这一点，然后Oz会走，&#39;让我们再次启动机器，然后再进行一次巡回演出。&#39; </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGD5OONT0Kp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,