nme.com/news/film/selena-gomez-kurt-cobain-nirvana-zoe-saldana-emilia-perez-3812058">在这里阅读<em>NME</em>与Gomez和Saldaña的完整聊天</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-drops-unreleased-track-stained-from-nine-years-ago-3848597">塞莱娜·戈麦斯（Selena Gomez）帖子在九年前从未发行的曲目“染色”中掉下来，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
